{"tid":1301582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]觀塘要人","createTime":"2019-07-09T16:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T17:49:41.000Z","uid":23653,"like":60,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"85cf5130dbd24bc5ab6c61d76627f91fd97c57f9","tid":1301582,"uid":23653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好對唔住各位巴打絲打， <br />\n我用一個咁嘅標題呃你哋入嚟，<br />\n簡單嚟講就係我喺觀塘月華街通往港鐵站嘅天橋整咗連儂牆，<br />\n但喺短短一個鐘就畀建制派支持者拆咗，希望各位可以嚟支援，<br />\n至於事情嘅始末就請睇以下內文：<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆位置：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZj8ZK5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZj8ZK5.jpg&h=1d29c856&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n <br />\n我係一位住咗喺觀塘月華街十五年左右嘅居民， <br />\n我哋嘅區議會長年被建制派控制， <br />\n每逢大時大節，<br />\n區議會就會喺通往港鐵站嘅天橋舉辦活動，<br />\n擋住居民嘅出入，<br />\n而選舉前後，<br />\n就會有極其擾民嘅宣傳車無限Loop投謝偉俊/徐海山一票，<br />\n但當我哋有問題需要兩位議員幫手嘅時候，永遠搵唔到佢哋，<br />\n無論係喺地鐵站附近發現為數唔少嘅針筒，<br />\n或是征求舊樓維修嘅意見，<br />\n甚至康寧道、物華街一帶充滿企街影響市容嘅問題，<br />\n我投訴幾多次都冇人跟進、處理。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因此我同一眾住喺觀塘月華街嘅青年人都非常渴求改變，<br />\n而今我哋見到有一位區內人士有意參選，<br />\n佢租咗一塊地產代理嘅廣告牌做宣傳，<br />\n希望宣揚自己嘅政綱、理念，<br />\n但我哋區內嘅親建制街坊就一次又一次作出毀壞行為，<br />\n那怕我每日都會經過哩塊廣告牌，<br />\n但我到今日都未見到哩位參選人嘅完整宣傳單張。<br />\n<br />\n所以我喺今日踏出咗第一步，整咗連儂牆，<br />\n希望可以話畀哩區嘅街坊聽哩個香港發生緊咩事，<br />\n同時我哋哩一區可以變得更好，<br />\n但估唔到短短一個鐘就畀人拆咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n因此希望各位住喺觀塘嘅巴絲打可以嚟幫幫手。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"555ff304b4f002ebd45a89831dd47acc6b2578c1","tid":1301582,"uid":23653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:31:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40641a6f4f5487cad74004213e5450967286dc92","tid":1301582,"uid":200758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:32:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AiR3F8V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAiR3F8V.jpg&h=f4a2740b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuDmAd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuDmAd2.jpg&h=28455d55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b11c7c1ccc512fb947454c04b063b69ec4154581","tid":1301582,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:32:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f88bb63c49f2d0c2b96427816282feb39e7f75f","tid":1301582,"uid":23653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:32:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f65fadf395443c2b0bcd3248cbdb97a0b0f6b8c9","tid":1301582,"uid":23653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:33:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6232c3a2581b2c299dd4e81405de862b33c4cd6f","tid":1301582,"uid":23653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:33:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf25c66d0f25e510b14f85610e67d78bff79a8a3","tid":1301582,"uid":23653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:34:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9173603f2c7e7fd0b098d559988781e3b61735c2","tid":1301582,"uid":23189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:34:23.000Z","msg":"入嚟討論下啦，有講點守連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「長文慎入」勇武又好、和理非又好，自己香港自己救！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299934</a>"},{"pid":"d2a37a2afd25bccb8c75a2880de34868199bec96","tid":1301582,"uid":23653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:34:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac9ad3f4138e5dd188b97e3eeffb1b9c3fbe2a7e","tid":1301582,"uid":23653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:3