if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開個新既<br />\n呢個唔好再覆<br />\n集火推另一個"},{"pid":"529f907d60e478324f3ed1efa5ad0caf22dd1324","tid":1301582,"uid":164646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f6b410ef8dd8026db1ed2dcf47584ec0ac56e98","tid":1301582,"uid":23653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1cb32af62d185f0fa4b4f1830b57c0aa2dd870bf","tid":1301582,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:38:43.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n巴打你呢d topic遲早狼來了<br />\n你不如轉個好d topic再開新post啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:41:03.000Z","msg":"對唔住巴打，<br />\n我啱啱落樓見到自己辛辛苦苦整嘅筆筒、Memo紙架畀人拆曬就火遮眼出咗哩個Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n諗得唔夠仔細，對唔住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:42:33.000Z","msg":"你試吓下晝放工加夜晚時段做Lennon Wall<br />\n應該效果會好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"800a383c9a72ae48ddd5a13b08f176d505c7f712","tid":1301582,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85cf5130dbd24bc5ab6c61d76627f91fd97c57f9","tid":1301582,"uid":23653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好對唔住各位巴打絲打， <br />\n我用一個咁嘅標題呃你哋入嚟，<br />\n簡單嚟講就係我喺觀塘月華街通往港鐵站嘅天橋整咗連儂牆，<br />\n但喺短短一個鐘就畀建制派支持者拆咗，希望各位可以嚟支援，<br />\n至於事情嘅始末就請睇以下內文：<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆位置：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZj8ZK5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZj8ZK5.jpg&h=1d29c856&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n <br />\n我係一位住咗喺觀塘月華街十五年左右嘅居民， <br />\n我哋嘅區議會長年被建制派控制， <br />\n每逢大時大節，<br />\n區議會就會喺通往港鐵站嘅天橋舉辦活動，<br />\n擋住居民嘅出入，<br />\n而選舉前後，<br />\n就會有極其擾民嘅宣傳車無限Loop投謝偉俊/徐海山一票，<br />\n但當我哋有問題需要兩位議員幫手嘅時候，永遠搵唔到佢哋，<br />\n無論係喺地鐵站附近發現為數唔少嘅針筒，<br />\n或是征求舊樓維修嘅意見，<br />\n甚至康寧道、物華街一帶充滿企街影響市容嘅問題，<br />\n我投訴幾多次都冇人跟進、處理。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因此我同一眾住喺觀塘月華街嘅青年人都非常渴求改變，<br />\n而今我哋見到有一位區內人士有意參選，<br />\n佢租咗一塊地產代理嘅廣告牌做宣傳，<br />\n希望宣揚自己嘅政綱、理念，<br />\n但我哋區內嘅親建制街坊就一次又一次作出毀壞行為，<br />\n那怕我每日都會經過哩塊廣告牌，<br />\n但我到今日都未見到哩位參選人嘅完整宣傳單張。<br />\n<br />\n所以我喺今日踏出咗第一步，整咗連儂牆，<br />\n希望可以話畀哩區嘅街坊聽哩個香港發生緊咩事，<br />\n同時我哋哩一區可以變得更好，<br />\n但估唔到短短一個鐘就畀人拆咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n因此希望各位住喺觀塘嘅巴絲打可以嚟幫幫手。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:42:42.000Z","msg":"有無tg"},{"pid":"720fabbafabe28be80a6daab30e19ce352f638c2","tid":1301582,"uid":23653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9737898131933d438b384078c735040ec1c34c87","tid":1301582,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"231a5984d172fe569f2888bebc4933a857e531a9","tid":1301582,"uid":23653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d7a392f8a32287477dfe061ffd3bed49bd8fff5","tid":1301582,"uid":204401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:38:18.000Z","msg":"觀塘A岀口有新連儂牆"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:39:36.000Z","msg":"美沙酮下面嗰個？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:41:01.000Z","msg":"應該APM下面果個<br />\n集中搞果個好過啦,月華街呢啲純住宅區比廢老拆都可預計得到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:43:21.000Z","msg":"上年月華區泛民都係輸畀建制一千票，應該有救架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89aa9ebdcd6ed0edcee53fe693536773b291c925","tid":1301582,"uid":23653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9623ae089b66cdac16a98ce8c81d54c5a628ac4a","tid":1301582,"uid":164646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply