es/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因此我同一眾住喺觀塘月華街嘅青年人都非常渴求改變，<br />\n而今我哋見到有一位區內人士有意參選，<br />\n佢租咗一塊地產代理嘅廣告牌做宣傳，<br />\n希望宣揚自己嘅政綱、理念，<br />\n但我哋區內嘅親建制街坊就一次又一次作出毀壞行為，<br />\n那怕我每日都會經過哩塊廣告牌，<br />\n但我到今日都未見到哩位參選人嘅完整宣傳單張。<br />\n<br />\n所以我喺今日踏出咗第一步，整咗連儂牆，<br />\n希望可以話畀哩區嘅街坊聽哩個香港發生緊咩事，<br />\n同時我哋哩一區可以變得更好，<br />\n但估唔到短短一個鐘就畀人拆咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n因此希望各位住喺觀塘嘅巴絲打可以嚟幫幫手。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:42:42.000Z","msg":"有無tg"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:48:23.000Z","msg":"@SHarunaLihkg"},{"pid":"4be4437afec0140f4fc715243cc6a5a007744160","tid":1301582,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4895c978c0cc78cf3221f6bfe8254c6f8238cd3d","tid":1301582,"uid":36722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:48:31.000Z","msg":"認同,集中力量搞呢到好過"},{"pid":"5b8614f4616809acf6f450156d4960b5b71b7cc4","tid":1301582,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:48:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48ba8d491c25a58d3e1dc2de8cdd19a401a997d3","tid":1301582,"uid":227174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07cd956e1b8b26d6587fe421704c5c17066f815a","tid":1301582,"uid":23653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17ba56670bbca00fefbf4c7c878d33f5a8ed478d","tid":1301582,"uid":227174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:41:40.000Z","msg":"觀塘真係好難搞, 你以為建制票倉浪得虛名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n區議會97後就一直俾呢班真廢老騎劫足咁多年<br />\n真廢老過多幾年收皮仲有SMP班支那大媽<br />\n年年選區議員票數都差幾條街<br />\n利申持BNO觀塘選民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" clas